{"id":179182,"type":1,"name":"¥十億少女","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/55/ed/179182_cXUJK.jpg","summary":"       大叶鹿子是和果子屋的三女，个性单纯迟钝，长相毫不起眼，总是被身边的人任意使唤。某天，大叶家负债累累的事实突然爆发，债主北条大我要求以大叶家的女儿抵债，於是鹿子16岁就以十亿元为代价出嫁。两人的婚姻生活风波不断，鹿子的同学鸠彦、忍成千方百计要帮她脱离困境，大我的背景又相当复杂。生於超级豪门却是个官能小说家，因母亲与双胞胎姐姐的丈夫私通而出生，曾被阿姨长期施以虐待，同父异母、长相和大我一模一样的礼王对他充满怨恨…","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>十亿少女</li><li><span>册数: </span>10</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/23103\">酒井美羽</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/518\">角川書店</a>、<a href=\"/person/7033\">東立出版社</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/8635\">MELODY</a>→<a href=\"/person/8516\">月刊Asuka</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>10亿少女</li><li><span>开始: </span>1999年5月号</li><li><span>结束: </span>2004年9月号</li>","collection":{"wish":1,"collect":1},"tags":[{"name":"已完结","count":1},{"name":"漫画系列","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":23103,"image":"","name":"酒井美羽","desc":"作者"},{"id":518,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/5a/52/518_prsn_ZwMWM.jpg","name":"角川书店","desc":"出版社"},{"id":7033,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/fd/24/7033_prsn_J3N83.jpg","name":"东立出版社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8635,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/68/d7/8635_prsn_6T0KE.jpg","name":"MELODY","desc":"连载杂志"},{"id":8516,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/15/13/8516_prsn_pKJG1.jpg","name":"月刊Asuka","desc":"连载杂志"}],"comic":[{"id":179175,"name":"¥十億少女 (1)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/47/c5/179175_jp.jpg"},{"id":179177,"name":"¥十億少女 (2)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/"},{"id":179178,"name":"¥十億少女 (3)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/8d/fb/179178_jp.jpg"},{"id":179179,"name":"¥十億少女 (4)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/08/c8/179179_jp.jpg"},{"id":179181,"name":"¥十億少女 (5)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/f1/74/179181_jp.jpg"},{"id":179180,"name":"¥十億少女 (6)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/b9/96/179180_jp.jpg"},{"id":179176,"name":"¥十億少女 (7)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/2d/76/179176_jp.jpg"},{"id":179173,"name":"¥十億少女 (8)","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/c/cf/18/179173_jp.jp